data.title: Communities
data.text:
Situated on the southeast edge of Richmond, Indiana, Forest Glen Estates is a private, gated subdivision conveniently located to shopping, dining, and entertainment. There are large, wooded lots with underground city utilities. A quiet, upscale lifestyle awaits you in Forest Glen.

Build your home and live surrounded by nature in Richmond’s beautiful, newest and most sought after subdivision – Honeysuckle Estates. Enjoy the serenity of the Honeysuckle waterfall.

Meadow Park is a fashionable neighborhood situated on the southeast side of Richmond, Indiana near shopping, dining, and entertainment.

Conveniently located on the southeast side of Richmond, Indiana, just minutes from dining and shopping. The large lots have all city utilities.

Our newest community featuring a quiet cul-de-sac nestled on the southeast side of historical Hagerstown. The rolling lots are large with mature trees.

Located on south edge of Centerville this affordable neighborhood is within walking distance to the schools. City streets with Street lights and sidewalks and city utilities are available.

Located along the Cardinal Greenway, Carrington Woods provides homeowners with unparalleled opportunities. Cardinal Greenway is the longest linear park in the state of Indiana, spanning more than 30 miles.

Situated on 147 acres of rolling, partially-wooded land, this magnificent development offers walking trails, park, club house, sidewalks, underground city utilities, a 15-acre lake plus a private lake, and a homeowner's association.
